Package: libgpgme++2
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Replaces: kdepimlibs5 (<< 4:4.4.0)
Breaks: kdepimlibs5 (<< 4:4.4.0)
Description: c++ wrapper library for gpgme
